bjhong02 wrote:

&gt;
&gt; I developed a filter to limit crawl to ranges of ip addresses. In
&gt; 1.2.0, there&#39;s a member function getServer() in class CrawURI, so I
&gt; can get IP address by ((CrawlURI)o).getServer().getHost().getIP() .
&gt;
&gt; But, in 1.3.0 there&#39;s no such function. How can I do this?

You must now go via the CrawlController to get the ServerCache 
instance.  Do something like:

 getController().getServerCache().getHostFor(curi).getIP()

In a filter, to get at the controller, you may have to do something like:

getSettingsHandler().getOrder().getController()

Hope this helps.

